.row
	.col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
		.row
			.col-md-12.text-center
				h2.text-primary
					|Log in
		.row
			.row
				form(ng-submit='logInToServer()')
					input.form-control(ng-focus='true' type='text' placeholder='Password' ng-model='password')
			p.text-warning
				| Do not share your credentials to anybody!
			.alert.alert-danger(ng-cloak ng-if='alert')
				| Login credentials are false, try a different password